00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:01,600
Could crayfish feel anxiety?

2
00:00:01,600 --> 00:00:03,200
New studies say yes.

3
00:00:03,200 --> 00:00:07,200
Researchers found crayfish showing signs of anxiety-like behavior when stressed.

4
00:00:07,200 --> 00:00:11,200
They responded to anti-anxiety drugs, similar to how humans do.

5
00:00:11,200 --> 00:00:15,600
But remember, this research is preliminary and still needs careful interpretation.

6
00:00:15,600 --> 00:00:20,400
Understanding these behaviors helps us learn about the emotional lives of animals.

